<div class="comment-text">
<p>One thing that isn’t clear from the article is the situation in life of the employees of Amazon.  The writer of the article clearly was working at Amazon temporarily, on his way on to better things. Could it be that the majority of these warehouse workers were doing the same thing?<br/>
